    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Some bloggers, for example, want to have thousands of followers. I’m okay with ten.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Some people get a kick out of running 42 whole kilometers. Other people find joy in walking one.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Many people won’t be happy unless they make over 80K this year, but others are perfectly fine with around 50.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And some businesses want to scale to infinity, while others are intentionally and happily small.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The point is not to feel bad (or to shame people) because ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "your",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " definition of ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "enough",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " is bigger or smaller than others’.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://pjrvs.com/enough"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s to decide on what your enough is. And to embrace the fact that your enough is enough, for you.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
